1711
01:57:52.527 --> 01:57:55.163
<i>...menyingkir dari
cahaya kebenaran.</i>


1712
01:57:56.564 --> 01:57:59.835
<i>Tak ada manusia,
tak ada hal mitos...</i>


1713
01:58:00.935 --> 01:58:05.407
