1729
01:58:54.288 --> 01:59:02.797
<i>"5 bulan kemudian, Lyndon Johnson ttd UU hak
memilih 1965 bersama Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr."</i>


1730
01:58:57.725 --> 01:59:00.228
